This paper is about a toolkit for Neural Machine Translation, which is a subfield of Natural Language Processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of neural networks, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of image captioning, which falls under cs.CV (Computer Vision).
